column5: To all of my US family and friends. Enjoy a great day with YOUR family and friends.
For some reason,I have the need for RED BEANS AND RICE.  Hope ya all have ya a great day.
Move farther away from the city me brudder. Your diet is starting to resemble that of a carp's.
Go for it RBR is one of the best meals you can make. Thanks for the well wishes we are heading down to Joes this evening for a grilling feast.   Art
Joe just PM'd me and said to tell you to pick him a bunch of beans on the way in.
